import numpy as np

def score(item, bins):
    max_capacity = np.max(bins)
    scores = np.zeros_like(bins)
    
    mask = bins != max_capacity

    return scores

import numpy as np

def score(item, bins):
    max_capacity = np.max(bins)
    scores = np.empty_like(bins)
    
    diff = bins - item
    diff[diff <= 0] = 1
    scores = bins / diff * (np.arange(len(bins)) + 1)
    scores[bins == max_capacity] = -1
    
    return scores

def score(item, bins):

    scores = np.zeros_like(bins)

    mask = bins != max_capacity

import numpy as np

def score(item, bins):
    num_bins = len(bins)
    normalized_capacity = 1 - (bins / np.max(bins))
    scores = np.power(normalized_capacity, num_bins) * np.arange(num_bins, 0, -1)
    return scores
